title: Understanding the economic impact of Brexit in tech, media, and telecom
itunes:title: Understanding the economic impact of Brexit in tech, media, and telecom
description: The UK is scheduled to leave the EU in just a few short months. And there are still a lot of unanswered questions. From supply chain to talent, which changes from Brexit could have the biggest impact on the TMT industry?
